******
[2] Kosovo
Date: Sun 27 Mar 2016
Source: Albeu [edited]
http://english.albeu.com/news/news/4-cases-of-suspected-swine-flu-in-kosovo/238684/


Swine flu cases have appeared again in Kosovo, where according to health authorities, 4 people are suspected of having the H1N1 virus.

One of these cases has already been diagnosed and admitted to the infectious clinic, while 3 others are waiting for the tests results.

"Yesterday [26 Mar 2016] we received one case, 2 today, quite typical, of having the H1N1 infection. We have a state of alert in the intensive care unit, " said Avdush Bajgora, one of the doctors.

